      <title>《时空恋旅人》观后感</title>
      <link href="/posts/202207_56729.html"/>
      <url>/posts/202207_56729.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>时空恋旅人 About Time 。一部现在才看的2013年的英国电影。</p><div class="douban-card-block">    <a class="douban-card" href="https://movie.douban.com/subject/10577869">        <div class="douban-card-bgimg" style="background-image: url('https://images.weserv.nl/?url=https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2070153774.jpg');"></div>        <div class="douban-card-left">            <div class="douban-card-img" style="background-image: url('https://images.weserv.nl/?url=https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2070153774.jpg');"></div>            <div class="douban-card-status">灯影绰约</div>        </div>        <div class="douban-card-right">            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>电影名: </span><strong>时空恋旅人AboutTime(2013)</strong></div>            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>导演: </span><span>理查德·柯蒂斯</span></div>            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>主演: </span><span>多姆纳尔·格里森/瑞秋·麦克亚当斯</span></div>            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>上映时间: </span><span>2013-09-04(英国)</span></div>            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>评分: </span><span>8.8</span></div>        </div>    </a></div><style>    .douban-card-block {    display: flex;    justify-content: center;    align-items: center;    width: 100%;    max-height: 400px;}.douban-card {    display: flex;    margin: 30px 10px;    padding: 15px;    border-radius: 15px;    position: relative;    justify-content: center;    align-items: center;    overflow: hidden;    color: antiquewhite;    text-decoration: none;}.douban-card:hover {    text-decoration: none;}.douban-card-bgimg {    position: absolute;    width: 115%;    height: 115%;    filter: blur(15px) brightness(0.6);    background-size: 100%;    background-position: center;    background-repeat: no-repeat;}.douban-card-img {    position: relative;    height: 130px;    width: 80px;    background-size: 100%;    background-position: center;    background-repeat: no-repeat;}.douban-card-left:hover .douban-card-img {    filter: blur(5px) brightness(0.6);    transform: perspective(800px) rotateX(180deg);}.douban-card-left .douban-card-img {    transition: all 500ms ease;}.douban-card-left {    position: relative;    display: flex;    flex-direction: column;    align-items: center;}.douban-card-left .douban-card-status {    height: 130px;    width: 80px;    text-align: center;    font-weight: bold;    position: absolute;    left: 0;    top: 30%;    transform: rotateX(180deg);    backface-visibility: hidden;    transition: all 500ms ease;}.douban-card-left:hover .douban-card-status {    transform: perspective(800px) rotateX(0deg);}.douban-card-right {    position: relative;    display: flex;    flex-direction: column;    margin-left: 12px;    font-size: 16px;    font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;    line-height: 1.3;    color: antiquewhite;}.douban-card-item {    margin-top: 4px;}</style><p>片中的男主角家族中的男性都具备闪回过去的能力，感觉如果让美国来拍那就是《回到未来》、《闪电侠》这类常见的美式drama，主人公都会利用自己的超能力来拯救世界最后抱得美人归。但是Tim显然有着平常人的脑回路：用它来找一个女朋友。</p><p>作为观众，这部电影让我们不必过于担心蝴蝶效应，不用担心男女主角的世界线波动，不必担心主角滥用能力进入时间循环，也不用担心“好坏守恒定律”。我们只需带着对生活的感受，镜头语言会告诉我们想要的一切。</p><p>如果我也有这种奇妙的能力，我会拿来做什么呢？男主的父亲给出了答案：<del>回去把所有想看的书都看两遍，狄更斯的看三遍。</del>把每一天都过两遍。第一遍是紧张，第二遍则会“看见”生活中不一样的东西。当然，我们的主人公找到了更好的答案：仔细且认真地度过每一天。</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/09/P8IlATQnv14FVi9.png" title="时空恋旅人"></p><p>珍惜生命中的每一天，细心品味生活中的美好。</p>]]></content>
      
      
